      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>720 - Added Entry-Uncontrolled Name (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">February 1999</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
