            <td colspan="1">$a - Name (NR) <br>$e - Relator term (R) <br>$4 - Relator code (R) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
         </tr>
